<L>__{interior evening. thornfield the third floor}
<A>__{rochester opens the door to the inner chamber.}
<C>__{mrs fairfax }
<D>__{... the mad lady must have stolen her keys and let herself out.}
<A>__{bertha antoinetta mason, standing in the last patch of daylight thrown down from her skylight, sees that it is rochester. she calmly walks towards him. rochester graciously bows, indicating that she may leave. bertha glides past him. she is free.}
